data.description:
This charming Bungalow offers a blend of comfort and convenience. This classic home beams with historic hardwood floors, large baseboard moldings and original French kitchen door. The open floor plan provides ample space for your family. Enjoy the spacious backyard, that backs up to wooded tree line.
Conveniently located in the heart of Blacksburg, this property allows for easy access to interstate I-85. Centrally located between Greenville & Charlotte. Only 41 Minutes to Charlotte Douglas Airport
Don't miss the opportunity to call 405 W Lime Street home. Schedule a showing today and experience the comfort and lifestyle this property has to offer!" Perfect Starter Home for first time home buyer
